---
title: Crispy Buffalo-Spiced Chicken with Blue Cheese Sauce, Scallion Mashed Potatoes & Parsnips
description: Are you the type who only goes to sporting events for Buffalo wings? We’re with you, and so we’ve taken the beloved dish from messy app to epic weeknight dinner. Chicken is brushed with sour cream, coated in a Buffalo-spiced panko mixture, roasted to juicy, crunchy perfection, and then drizzled with creamy blue cheese sauce. Roasted parsnips and sour cream-scallion mashed potatoes on the side make this dish a slam dunk.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651afb03f8c6c435c24a9129-5044291e.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/651afb03f8c6c435c24a9129.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
